      • readField

        private static void readField(java.lang.Object[] vals,
                              int fieldIdx,
                              org.apache.orc.TypeDescription schema,

                              int childCount)
        Reads a vector of data into an array of objects.
        参数:
        vals - The array that needs to be filled.
        fieldIdx - If the vals array is an array of Row, the index of the field that needs to be filled. Otherwise a -1 must be passed and the data is directly filled into the array.
        schema - The schema of the vector to read.
        vector - The vector to read.
        childCount - The number of vector entries to read.

        Sets a repeating value to all objects or row fields of the passed vals array.
        参数:
        vals - The array of objects or Rows.
        fieldIdx - If the objs array is an array of Row, the index of the field that needs to be filled. Otherwise a -1 must be passed and the data is directly filled into the array.
        repeatingValue - The value that is set.
        childCount - The number of times the value is set.
